doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title Account Verification - Action Required
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #444444;
      }

      a.button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
  body
    h2 Account Verification - Action Required
    p Dear #{username},
    p Thank you for creating an account with us. To complete the email verification process and activate your account, please click the button below:
    p
      a.button(href=[appUrl, 'api', 'v1', 'auth', 'verify?hash=' + hash].join('/')) Verify Email Address
    p By clicking the above button, you will be redirected to our website to verify your email address. This verification step ensures the security and validity of your account.
    p If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following URL into your web browser:
    p= [appUrl, 'api', 'v1', 'auth', 'verify?hash=' + hash].join('/')
    p Please note that the verification link is time-sensitive and will expire after 24 hours.
    p Thank you for choosing System of Santri. We look forward to providing you with a secure and enjoyable experience on our platform.
    p
      | Best regards,
      br
      | System of Santri
      br
      | Pondok Programmer